content.value: Start the Salary Updating Process
Initiate a process for periodic or personal salary adjustments for your employees, and get adjustment offers from managers for their subordinates.
All-in-One Employee Performance Management
Engage with your employees and reflect on individual performance based on competency, on goal, or both.
Digitalize Salary Evaluation Processes
Manage and report the salary evaluation and update operations of your employees until the leading manager's approval.
Create the Process Management Structure
Include all of your employees in the process, from functional managers to the leading manager's approval, and set up the evaluation hierarchy.
360-Degree Feedback
Implement a 360-degree performance management system and get formal feedback from peers & managers.
Competence Assessment
Evaluate employee competency including leadership qualities, communication skills, productivity, and more.
Goal-Based Evaluation
Measure company performance with more concrete data.
Access Employee Records Anytime, from Anywhere
Access to your employees' data from your desktop or mobile devices, and avoid time and effort loss.
Evaluate and Approve Edits
Approve or request for reconsideration of salary increase offers from the head of department.
Manage Leave and Overtime Online
Track leave requests, and overtime data effortlessly.
Private Account for Each Employee
Employees can request their needs through their private accounts using Easy HR's desktop or mobile applications.
Manage Your Employee Data in One Organized and Secure Database
Employee records, leaves, expenses, overtime management, debts, training, and much more. Online, fast, and secure.
The best way to handle all of your employee data in one place.
Setting up new employees? Payroll? Filling in time sheets? Easily manage employee data and tasks in one place
The easiest way to manage employee data
The HR software thats easy to use, and gives you the power to make meaningful change.
